The paper discusses privacy preservation methods for data streams, which falls under the category of computer security (cs.CR) and database systems (cs.DB). The proposed method also involves machine learning techniques for accurate data stream mining, which relates to topics in machine learning (cs.LG) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI). Finally, the paper mentions efficiency and scalability issues, which could also be relevant to the field of data structures and algorithms (cs.DS).
